com.facebook.react.devsupport.interfaces

Interface DevSupportManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NativeModuleCallExceptionHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DevSupportManagerImpl, DisabledDevSupportManager

    public interface DevSupportManager
extends NativeModuleCallExceptionHandler
    Interface for accessing and interacting with development features. In dev mode, use the implementation DevSupportManagerImpl. In production mode, use the dummy implementation DisabledDevSupportManager.
